{"id":251463,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/09/维权网-天津近百访民到达沃斯会场诉冤情（图）/","date":"2012-09-13T19:01:00Z","modified":"2012-09-13T19:01:00Z","title":"维权网 | 天津近百访民到达沃斯会场诉冤情（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><br /><span>（维权网信息员徐增泉报道）达沃斯会议</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>日</span><span>至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>日在天津梅江会展中心召开。百余访民为诉冤情而前往会场，有访民因此被限制人身自由。</span></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>访民的这一行动被数百警察驱赶，许多访民被警方用大客车强行拉到几公里以外的市政府信访处进行登记。然而访民们早已习惯了这种到信访办登记的欺骗的把戏，访民们不买账，随后又都返回会场诉冤情和抗议。访民们如此往返会场直到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>号的晚</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>点多才结束。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>号和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>号仍有大批访民前去会场诉冤情。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>警方为阻止访民们再返回会场，将在信访登记处的访民非法拘禁数小时，直到有访民所属派出所人员来接才获自由。访民被非法控制几个小时期间，没有水，没有饭提供给访民。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span><br /><span><br /></span></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-XE25v19GewM/UFIG1a6KLZI/AAAAAAAAOPc/OcPLrzB2Kvo/s1600/%E5%A4%A9%E6%B4%A5%E6%8A%93%E8%AE%BF%E6%B0%91%E7%9A%84%E8%AD%A6%E8%BD%A6.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"216\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-XE25v19GewM/UFIG1a6KLZI/AAAAAAAAOPc/OcPLrzB2Kvo/s320/%E5%A4%A9%E6%B4%A5%E6%8A%93%E8%AE%BF%E6%B0%91%E7%9A%84%E8%AD%A6%E8%BD%A6.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>天津抓访民的警车</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-5510311487081677871?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#03